- rule_name: SANCT_ALLOWANCE_RACE
  severity: Warning
  message: "SANCT_ALLOWANCE_RACE: `approve` overwrites the allowance at key `(owner . clone () , spender . clone ())` unconditionally from a caller-supplied amount, enabling the approve front-running race"
